{%- if reminder_type == 'pre_due' -%}
UPCOMING PAYMENT DUE

This is a friendly reminder that invoice {{ invoice.invoiceId }} is due in {{ days_until_due }} {{ days_until_due == 1 ? 'day' : 'days' }}. We wanted to give you advance notice to make payment arrangements convenient.
{%- elseif reminder_type == 'overdue_1' -%}
PAYMENT REMINDER

Invoice {{ invoice.invoiceId }} became overdue yesterday. If you've already sent payment, please disregard this reminder. Otherwise, we'd appreciate your prompt attention to settle this invoice.
{%- elseif reminder_type == 'overdue_7' -%}
PAYMENT OVERDUE

Invoice {{ invoice.invoiceId }} is now 7 days overdue. Please arrange payment at your earliest convenience. If there are any issues preventing payment, please contact us so we can help resolve them.
{%- elseif reminder_type == 'overdue_14' -%}
URGENT: IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED

Invoice {{ invoice.invoiceId }} remains unpaid after 14 days. This is our final automated reminder. Immediate payment is required to avoid service interruption. Please contact us if you need to discuss payment arrangements.
{%- else -%}
INVOICE REMINDER

This is a reminder about invoice {{ invoice.invoiceId }}.
{%- endif -%}

Invoice Details:
----------------
Invoice Number: {{ invoice.invoiceId }}
{% if invoice.invoiceDate %}
Invoice Date: {{ invoice.invoiceDate|date('Y-m-d') }}
{% endif %}
{% if invoice.due %}
Due Date: {{ invoice.due|date('Y-m-d') }}
{% endif %}
{% if invoice.balance %}
Amount Due: {{ invoice.balance|formatCurrency(invoice.client.currency) }}
{% endif %}

{%- if reminder_type == 'pre_due' -%}
Thank you for your business. We appreciate prompt payment.
{%- else -%}
We appreciate your immediate attention to this matter.
{%- endif %}

View Invoice: {{ url("_view_invoice_external", {"uuid" : invoice.uuid}) }}

If you have any questions or concerns about this invoice, please don't hesitate to contact us.
